<cell id="cell-16-md"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type>### Mini-smoke (10 real prompts, optional but recommended)

The pytest above uses dummy "hi" prompts. This runs 5 real GRPO steps on K&K puzzles to surface reward-signal issues (e.g. all-zero rewards) before the full run.

**Expected:** reward_mean > 0 (model gets some format reward). If reward_mean is 0 across all 5 steps, the reward parser isn't matching the model's output — investigate before Stage B.</cell id="cell-16-md">

